name: Tiki Bros (Harbo)
description:
Tiki Bros was created as a major production course while in our first year at AIE (Academy of Interactive Entertainment) 

This project was created in six weeks with a team of 6 people. 

Designers: Georgia Bryant, Brodie Harbridge, Phillip Pajor.

Artists: Ashleigh Lamb, Niamh Thirlwell-Towler.

Programmer: Andrew Spencer
